### 🎨 Branding

This folder contains additional CSS tweaks that build on top of the **Ultrachromic** theme by CTalvio.

> ⚠️ **You need to apply the Ultrachromic base theme first before using these tweaks!**

**How to apply the base theme:**
1. Go to your Jellyfin **Admin Dashboard** in your web browser
2. Navigate to **Dashboard → General → Branding**
3. Paste the following code into the **Custom CSS** field:
```css
@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/CTalvio/Ultrachromic/presets/kaleidochromic_preset.css');
@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/CTalvio/Ultrachromic/header/header_transparent.css');
@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/CTalvio/Ultrachromic/login/login_minimalistic.css');
@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/CTalvio/Ultrachromic/progress/floating.css');
@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/CTalvio/Ultrachromic/effects/glassy.css');
@import url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/CTalvio/Ultrachromic/episodelist/episodes_compactlist.css');
@import url("https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/intro-skipper/intro-skipper-css@main/skip-button.min.css");

/* Home Tab */
.emby-tab-button.tab-home::before {
    content: "home";
    font-family: 'Material Icons';
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-right: 10px;
}

/* Favoriten Tab */
.emby-tab-button.tab-favorites::before {
    content: "favorite";
    font-family: 'Material Icons';
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-right: 10px;
}

/* Watchlist Tab */
.emby-tab-button.tab-watchlist::before {
    content: "bookmark";
    font-family: 'Material Icons';
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-right: 10px;
}

/* Bookmark+ Tab */
.emby-tab-button.tab-bookmarkadd::before {
    content: "bookmark_add";
    font-family: 'Material Symbols Rounded';
    font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-right: 10px;
}

:root {
    --skip-hide-duration: 8s;
}

4. Click **Save** and hard refresh your browser (Ctrl+Shift+R)

